release_note: Revamped Keyboard Menu Design: Experience a fresh and improved design with our re imagined keyboard menu. We ve prioritized ease of use to enhance your overall interaction and provide a seamless user experience. Optimized Performance and Bug Fixes: Our commitment to perfection continues with this update. We ve diligently addressed bugs and fine tuned performance to ensure a smoother and more reliable user experience. Enjoy a more polished and responsive app with this latest release.

Introducing Clipboards! Easily manage your copied text with the new Clipboard feature. Copy and paste clips or create Shortcuts for swift insertion. Enhanced Language Support: Now enjoy full text translation to English French Spanish Turkish Arabic German Dutch Japanese Korean Russian Swedish and Chinese. Bug Fixes and Performance Improvements: We ve resolved bugs and made enhancements for a smoother user experience.
